1
00:00:04,330 --> 00:00:06,660
Did everything go okay with the annulment?
手续办得还顺利吗？

2
00:00:06,940 --> 00:00:09,230
No problems. It's all taken care of.
没问题，都办好了 

3
00:00:09,440 --> 00:00:10,670
Ross,thank you.
罗斯，谢谢你

4
00:00:12,340 --> 00:00:13,900
Want to go see a movie?
你们要不要去看电影 

5
00:00:14,110 --> 00:00:15,100
Yeah,why not?
好啊

6
00:00:15,310 --> 00:00:16,800
I'll get my sweater.
