00:00:20,250 --> 00:00:21,810
Want to hear something weird?
想不想听一件奇怪的事？ 

8
00:00:22,020 --> 00:00:23,310
Always.
当然

9
00:00:24,990 --> 00:00:27,080
I didn't get the annulment.
我没去办注销

10
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:29,420
What?
什么？ 

11
00:00:29,620 --> 00:00:31,020
We're still married.
我们还是夫妻

12
00:00:32,360 --> 00:00:34,490
Don't tell Rachel. See you later.
不要告诉瑞秋，待会见

13
00:00:38,200 --> 00:00:39,830
Do you have any gum?
你有口香糖吗？

14
00:00:41,870 --> 00:00:45,770
Wait! Wait! Ross,can I just talk to you for just a second?
等等！ 罗斯，可以跟你谈一下吗？

15
00:00:46,010 --> 00:00:47,700
We'll be late for the movie.
