16
00:00:48,010 --> 00:00:49,770
There's a cab. Taxi!
那里有计程车，计程车

17
00:00:50,510 --> 00:00:52,100
That's great.

18
00:00:52,310 --> 00:00:54,940
What timing! My God,huh? There you go.
来得正好，上车吧

19
00:00:55,680 --> 00:00:58,350
We're gonna walk. It's right at the Angelika.
我们要走去前面的安洁丽戏院

20
00:00:58,620 --> 00:00:59,990
The Angelika! Go! Go!
安洁丽戏院，开车

21
00:01:02,290 --> 00:01:04,020
You didn't get the annulment?!
你没去注销？ 

22
00:01:04,230 --> 00:01:05,890
I know.
我知道

23
00:01:07,460 --> 00:01:10,860
I tried,but when I got to my lawyer's office, all I heard was:
我试过，但在律师楼我只听到

24
00:01:11,070 --> 00:01:13,590
"Three divorces! Three divorces!"
“离婚三次，离婚三次”

25
00:01:13,770 --> 00:01:17,070
Yes,in that high voice.
没错，是女高音

26
00:01:17,270 --> 00:01:21,800
I just don't want my tombstone to read: "Ross Geller: Three Divorces."
我不希望我的墓碑上刻着 “罗斯盖勒，离婚三次”

27
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:25,640
Don't worry about that. Your tombstone can say whatever you want.
你不必担心那个 你爱刻什么就刻什么

28
00:01:25,880 --> 00:01:28,580
It can say, "Ross Geller: Good at Marriage."
你可以刻 “罗斯盖勒，婚姻高手”

29
00:01:29,650 --> 00:01:33,950
You know? Mine's gonna say, "Phoebe Buffay: Buried Alive."
我的会刻 “菲比布非，活埋在此”

30
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:38,050
All I know is,I can't have another failed marriage.
反正我不能再添一次失败婚姻

31
00:01:38,290 --> 00:01:42,160
So you're gonna be married to a girl who doesn't even know about it?
所以你要娶个不知情的女生？

32
00:01:42,430 --> 00:01:44,230
Woman. Sorry.
女人，抱歉

33
00:01:46,270 --> 00:01:49,240
Okay,so I don't have it all worked out quite yet.
我还没想好要怎么做 

34
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:51,840
Just don't say anything to Rachel.
拜托你先别告诉瑞秋

35
00:01:52,070 --> 00:01:55,070
Rachel is one of my closest friends.
瑞秋是我最要好的朋友之一

36
00:01:55,310 --> 00:01:59,470
But being the only one that knows about this makes me feel special. Okay.
不过当唯一知情的人感觉不赖 好吧

37
00:02:02,450 --> 00:02:04,920
Okay,stop,stop! Phoebe?
停车 菲比？ 

38
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,520
Hey,Rach!
瑞秋

39
00:02:07,690 --> 00:02:09,250
What was that?
你在搞什么？ 

40
00:02:09,490 --> 00:02:11,080
Sorry. Mix-up.
抱歉，弄错了

41
00:02:12,190 --> 00:02:13,490
How was the movie?
电影好看吗？ 

42
00:02:14,260 --> 00:02:16,090
I haven't seen it yet.
我还没看

43
00:02:16,330 --> 00:02:18,460
You'd better hurry. The Angelika! Go!
那就要快了 安洁丽戏院，开车

44
00:02:19,272 --> 00:02:20,796
不…

