Did you tell him you're moving out?
你想好要怎么说了吗？ 

50
00:03:15,390 --> 00:03:18,690
No,I keep trying. And I can get out,"Joey,I have to.."
还没，我试了好几次 我只能说出“乔伊，我得…”

52
00:03:18,930 --> 00:03:22,860
Then I lose my nerve and I finish with, "go to the bathroom."
然后就退缩改说“去上厕所”

53
00:03:23,460 --> 00:03:24,930
He may think I'm sick.
他可能以为我有病

54
00:03:25,870 --> 00:03:29,390
I have to tell Rachel,but.... We just gotta get it over with.
我真的得告诉瑞秋了 早死早超生

55
00:03:29,600 --> 00:03:32,800
Next time we see them, we'll just tell them. That's it.
下次见到他们，我们就说

57
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:36,200
That's how it'll work now? You'll just order me around?
就这么决定 以后你都要这样指使我是吧？

59
