-Pretty much. -All right.
差不多 好

60
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:43,110
Hey,man,you feeling better?
摩妮卡 你有没有好一点？

62
00:03:48,090 --> 00:03:49,750
We have something to tell you.
乔伊，我们有事要说

63
