Oh,my God!
天哪

64
00:03:52,290 --> 00:03:53,990
You're pregnant!
你怀孕了

65
00:03:55,660 --> 00:03:57,290
No!
不是

66
00:03:57,503 --> 00:03:59,869
没有吧？不是

67
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,940
Look, Joe,here's the thing.
乔伊，是这样的

68
00:04:04,970 --> 00:04:08,740
Monica and I have decided to live together, here.
摩妮卡和我决定在这里同居 

69
00:04:09,610 --> 00:04:11,600
I'm gonna be moving out, man.
所以我会搬出来

71
00:04:18,950 --> 00:04:23,120
I'm really happy for you guys. Congratulations. See you later.
我真替你们高兴 恭喜，回见

72
00:04:24,190 --> 00:04:25,250
Are you okay?
等等，乔伊，你还好吗？

73
00:04:25,460 --> 00:04:27,930
I gotta go. I've got an acting job.
很好，我得走了，我有戏要演

74
00:04:30,100 --> 00:04:31,330
Like you'd believe that.
你们会信才怪

75
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:34,360
This sucks!
讨厌啦

76
00:04:34,870 --> 00:04:37,500
I'll be across the hall. And I promise you...
我只是要搬到对门，我保证

77
00:04:37,710 --> 00:04:41,270
the minute Monica and I break up, I'm moving right back in.
摩妮卡和我一分手 我就回去跟你住

78
00:04:42,340 --> 00:04:44,740
Maybe that's now.
你是说现在吗？

79
00:04:45,280 --> 00:04:47,270
If you're gonna move in with him...
好，如果你要跟他住 

80
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:50,850
I feel it is my responsibility to tell you the truth about him.
我有责任揭穿他的真面目

81
00:04:51,150 --> 00:04:53,250
He's a terrible roommate. Terrible.
他是个很烂的室友

82
00:04:53,450 --> 00:04:55,180
He forgets to....
他会忘记…

83
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:58,490
He always,he always....
他老是…

84
00:04:59,590 --> 00:05:01,530
Who am I kidding? He's the best roommate!
我骗谁啊，他最棒了

85
00:05:06,870 --> 00:05:08,700
-Hey,Phoebe. -Hey.
菲比

86
00:05:08,870 --> 00:05:12,600
Oh, look, here's an article about people who marry people and don't tell them.
有一篇文章在讨论 结了婚却不告诉对方的人

87
00:05:12,770 --> 00:05:16,300
-Really? -Yeah, I'm reading Ross Geller Magazine.
真的？ 对，我在看罗斯盖勒杂志

88
00:05:18,610 --> 00:05:19,600
Have you seen Rachel?
菲比，你有看到瑞秋吗？

89
00:05:19,780 --> 00:05:22,010
-No, why? -I have some exciting news.
没有，怎样？ 我有个好消息

90
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:23,680
You're pregnant.
你怀孕了

91
00:05:25,020 --> 00:05:26,540
No!
不是

92
00:05:27,620 --> 00:05:29,450
Chandler and I are moving in together.
钱德和我决定同居 

93
00:05:29,690 --> 00:05:31,250
Oh,that's good!
太好了

94
00:05:31,460 --> 00:05:35,190
But if you were pregnant, what would you name it?  Hint,Phoebe.
不过如果你有宝宝要叫什么？ 提示：菲比

95
00:05:39,070 --> 00:05:40,360
What's up?
怎么样？

96
00:05:42,300 --> 00:05:44,740
Chandler and I are moving in together.
钱德和我要住在一起

97
00:05:44,940 --> 00:05:47,100
Oh,my God.
天哪 

98
00:05:47,440 --> 00:05:50,970
Oh,my little sister and my best friend...
我妹妹和我的死党…

99
00:05:51,250 --> 00:05:52,800
shacking up.
搞在一起

100
00:05:54,550 --> 00:05:56,810
That's great. That's great.
太好了

101
00:05:57,490 --> 00:05:58,920
Guys, I'm happy too.
喂，我也很高兴 

102
00:05:59,220 --> 00:06:00,620
Okay,come here.
好，一起来

103
00:06:01,620 --> 00:06:06,220
Big day,huh? People moving in. People getting annulled.
今天真热闹 有人要同居，有人办注销

104
00:06:09,400 --> 00:06:11,260
I gotta go find Rachel.
我要去找瑞秋了，不过…

105
00:06:11,500 --> 00:06:15,830
If you see her,give her some really bad news, so mine doesn't seem so bad.
你们能不能先灌些坏消息给她 减轻一些冲击？

106
00:06:16,542 --> 00:06:17,600
再见

107
00:06:19,270 --> 00:06:21,610
Something bad to tell Rachel.
讲给瑞秋听的坏消息…

108
00:06:23,410 --> 00:06:25,810
Bad news for Rachel. What could that be?
什么是她的坏消息？

109
00:06:27,080 --> 00:06:29,350
Can you just lay off, please?
你能不能别再提了？

110
00:06:29,620 --> 00:06:34,150
My life is an embarrassment. I should just go live under somebody's stairs.
我的人生很难堪 我应该去住在别人的楼梯底下

111
00:06:34,990 --> 00:06:38,450
It's not that big a deal. You'll have been divorced three times.
根本没那么严重 离婚三次又怎样

113
00:06:38,690 --> 00:06:40,750
You'll have a life,you'll date..
你还是会有私生活、会约会…

114
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:45,160
No, I won't. I'll be at the bottom of the dating barrel now.
才不会 我的约会指数降到谷底

115
00:06:45,430 --> 00:06:48,160
The only guys below me will be Four-Divorce Guy...
比我低的只有离婚四次的人 

116
00:06:48,440 --> 00:06:50,430
Murderer Guy...
杀人犯和…

117
00:06:50,670 --> 00:06:52,330
and geologists.
地质学家

118
00:06:53,710 --> 00:06:57,700
Ross, you're being ridiculous. You are cute and smart and sweet.
罗斯，你别傻了 你可爱聪明又体帖

119
00:06:57,980 --> 00:07:01,110
That is much more important than three stupid divorces.
这比离婚三次重要多了

120
00:07:01,350 --> 00:07:04,340
Have you dated anyone who's been divorced three times?
是吗？ 你交过离婚三次的男朋友吗？

121
00:07:04,550 --> 00:07:08,890
That's not fair. Most guys that have been divorced three times are 60.
这样问不公平 离三次婚的人通常都60了

122
00:07:10,630 --> 00:07:12,390
You're young.
你多年轻啊

123
00:07:13,660 --> 00:07:15,790
That's true,I am young.
我是很年轻

124
00:07:15,960 --> 00:07:17,830
Well....

125
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:21,290
Nobody cares about this except you.
只有你自己在意 

126
00:07:21,500 --> 00:07:24,840
This embarrassment thing is all in your head.
什么难堪都是你在想像

127
00:07:25,840 --> 00:07:28,570
-Here,I'll show you. Come here. -What?
我证明给你看 过来 干嘛？

128
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:32,940
Hi. My friend Ross is about to be divorced for the third time.
我朋友罗斯即将三度离婚

130
00:07:33,180 --> 00:07:34,670
But wouldn't you date him?
但你们会和他约会吧？

131
00:07:35,950 --> 00:07:38,940
And if you wait right here, I'll go get Ross.
你们稍候，我去找罗斯来

132
00:07:43,890 --> 00:07:45,090
Thought you were Rachel.
我还以为你是瑞秋 

133
00:07:45,530 --> 00:07:47,360
What gave me away?
我哪里露出破绽了？

134
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:49,190
I gotta tell her.
我得赶快告诉她

135
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:51,630
I told Ross and Phoebe. She's the only one left.
我已经告诉罗斯和菲比 只剩她了

136
00:07:51,870 --> 00:07:54,460
It's official. We're moving in together.
所以大家都知道了 我们确定要同居了

137
00:07:54,740 --> 00:07:58,070
No turning back. Are you scared? Are you?!
不能反悔 你怕吗？怕吗？

138
00:07:59,270 --> 00:08:00,300
No.
不怕

139
00:08:00,580 --> 00:08:02,630
That was my scariest voice. You're brave.
那是我最可怕的声音 你真勇敢

140
00:08:07,550 --> 00:08:08,640
The worst day.
今天真惨

141
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:13,480
You're finally making progress at work, then your boss calls you Racquel.
你以为自己终于受重视了 结果老板却叫你拉蔻儿

142
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:18,820
Listen,for the first four years of my work, everybody called me....
我进公司前4年 大家都叫我夏拉拉

143
00:08:25,170 --> 00:08:27,160
-Seriously. -I believe you.
是真的 我相信

144
00:08:28,770 --> 00:08:32,600
It was in the middle of a meeting, so no one wants to correct her.
当时正在开员工大会 当然不会有人纠正她

145
00:08:32,810 --> 00:08:34,500
So everyone's calling me Racquel.
于是大家都叫我拉蔻儿

146
00:08:34,780 --> 00:08:38,440
By the end of the day,the mailroom guys were calling me Rocky.
到了下班前 收发室的人已经叫成洛基了

147
00:08:40,110 --> 00:08:43,640
Well,I still think you're very,very nice and very pretty.
我还是觉得你很好很漂亮

148
00:08:44,650 --> 00:08:45,680
What?
什么？

149
00:08:47,420 --> 00:08:48,910
All yours, babe.
交给你了

150
00:08:49,829 --> 00:08:51,524
瑞秋，过来

151
00:08:51,930 --> 00:08:52,950
Have a seat.
坐

152
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:57,330
Listen,Chandler and I...
听我说 钱德和我...

153
00:08:58,100 --> 00:08:59,960
are going to live together.
要一起住在...

154
00:09:00,300 --> 00:09:01,330
Here.
这里

155
00:09:04,670 --> 00:09:05,830
Oh,my God.
天哪

156
00:09:07,380 --> 00:09:08,870
That's so great!
真是太棒了

157
00:09:10,610 --> 00:09:13,010
I'm so happy for you guys!
我真替你们高兴

158
00:09:13,210 --> 00:09:14,310
Really?
真的？

159
00:09:14,620 --> 00:09:16,880
And that was so sweet of you to ask.
你真好，还先问我

160
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:21,020
The three of us are gonna have such a good time living together!
天哪 我们三个在一起一定会很开心

161
00:09:22,820 --> 00:09:23,950
Yes,we are.
是啊

162
00:09:25,030 --> 00:09:28,220
Chandler, you'll have to watch those long showers you take...
钱德，你早上不能慢慢冲澡了 

163
00:09:28,460 --> 00:09:31,400
because you know Racquel can't be late.
因为拉蔻儿不能迟到

164
00:09:33,130 --> 00:09:34,400
He'll work on that.
瑞秋 他会注意的

165
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:37,870
This is so exciting!
好兴奋喔

166
00:09:41,010 --> 00:09:43,340
Come and knock on our door
来敲我的门 （影集“三人行”主题曲）

167
00:09:45,650 --> 00:09:47,740
We'll be waiting for you
我们等着你

168
00:09:54,060 --> 00:09:57,050
See? Once you know the stories, it's not that bad.
一旦知道内情就没那么糟了

169
00:09:57,260 --> 00:10:00,820
First marriage: Wife's hidden sexuality. Not my fault.
第一次，老婆隐瞒性向 不是我的错

170
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:04,930
Second marriage: Said the wrong name at the altar.
第二次，宣誓时叫错人 

171
00:10:05,230 --> 00:10:06,890
A little my fault.
有一点点是我的错

172
00:10:08,170 --> 00:10:11,260
Third marriage: They shouldn't let you get married...
第三次 怎么能让...

174
00:10:11,540 --> 00:10:13,910
when you're drunk and have writing on your face.
脸上涂鸦的醉鬼结婚

175
00:10:14,110 --> 00:10:15,670
Nevada's fault.
内华达州的错

176
00:10:17,210 --> 00:10:21,170
