177
00:10:21,520 --> 00:10:23,850
The divorces don't bother me. I'd date him.
离婚无所谓，我会和他约会 

178
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:25,590
But not while he's still married.
但他得先恢复自由身

179
00:10:25,850 --> 00:10:27,840
And you,wouldn't you want to date?
那你呢？你也想吧？

180
00:10:28,090 --> 00:10:30,060
I'm not dating at all anymore.
事实上我再也不约会了

181
00:10:30,290 --> 00:10:32,890
