随便啦

184
00:10:37,570 --> 00:10:38,590
And you,Meg?
梅格你呢？

185
00:10:38,800 --> 00:10:41,600
Well,I don't care about the divorces, either.
我也不在意离婚的事 

186
00:10:41,800 --> 00:10:43,960
But I wouldn't date him.
但我不会和他约会

187
00:10:44,140 --> 00:10:47,940
Normally, he doesn't sweat this much.
他平常不会流这么多汗

188
00:10:48,210 --> 00:10:51,870
It's just that he's obviously still in love with this Rachel girl.
他显然还爱着这个瑞秋 

189
00:10:52,110 --> 00:10:53,240
What?
什么？

190
00:10:53,410 --> 00:10:57,010
She said,"He's obviously still in love with this Rachel girl."
她说 “他显然还爱着这个瑞秋”

191
00:10:59,850 --> 00:11:03,190
This is crazy. I mean, yes, Rachel is my good friend.
这话太扯了 没错，瑞秋是我的好朋友

192
00:11:03,420 --> 00:11:06,050
And I have loved her in the past...
我过去确实爱过她 

193
00:11:06,290 --> 00:11:08,590
but now, she is just my wife.
但现在她只是我的妻子

194
00:11:10,900 --> 00:11:13,030
Phoebe, will you help me out here?
菲比，帮我说句话好吗？

195
00:11:13,230 --> 00:11:16,260
Well, I thought you loved her when you married her.
你娶她时我也以为你爱她

196
00:11:16,540 --> 00:11:20,940
We were drunk! I would've married Joey with that amount of alcohol.
我们喝醉了 喝那么多我连乔伊都会娶

197
00:11:21,940 --> 00:11:24,640
You could do a lot worse than Joey Tribbiani!
比乔伊崔比亚尼烂的人多得是

198
00:11:27,150 --> 00:11:28,980
I'm sorry, but you guys are wrong.
很抱歉，但是你们错了 

199
00:11:29,220 --> 00:11:32,450
I just don't want to be divorced three times.
我只是不想离三次婚

200
00:11:32,650 --> 00:11:34,950
Now he's using this three-divorces reason...
没错，他以此为藉口...

201
00:11:35,220 --> 00:11:38,450
because he wants to stay married to her because he loves her.
不想离婚 因为他爱她

202
00:11:38,730 --> 00:11:41,160
I must say, well done. Bravo,Meg.
我必须说：梅格，干得好

203
00:11:42,830 --> 00:11:45,820
Fine. If this is what you think, forget about...
好，如果你们这么想 

204
00:11:46,070 --> 00:11:47,590
the whole three-divorce thing.
那我就不管了

205
00:11:47,800 --> 00:11:52,140
I'll go to my lawyer's office right now and get this marriage annulled.
我现在就去找律师办注销

206
00:11:52,340 --> 00:11:54,000
She means nothing to me.
因为我一点也不爱她 

207
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:56,140
Nothing!
一点也不爱

208
00:11:57,980 --> 00:12:01,740
Okay, now I wouldn't date you because you seem a little creepy.
现在是你的神经质让我发毛

209
00:12:02,180 --> 00:12:04,340
I am so attracted to him right now.
我突然觉得他好有魅力

210
00:12:09,760 --> 00:12:12,590
When will we tell Rachel what actually will happen?
我们什么时候要跟瑞秋说实话

211
00:12:12,760 --> 00:12:13,750
Soon.
快了

212
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:16,790
I just couldn't before. You saw how upset Joey got.
我刚才说不出口 你也看到乔伊多难过

213
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:19,330
I couldn't do it. She's my best friend.
我不忍心伤害我最好的朋友

214
00:12:19,530 --> 00:12:21,020
Joey's my best friend.
乔伊也是我最好的朋友

215
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:23,860
I'm not your best friend?
我不是吗？

216
00:12:25,270 --> 00:12:26,600
You just said..
你自己刚才说…

217
00:12:28,280 --> 00:12:30,330
Of course you're my best friend.
你当然是

218
00:12:31,310 --> 00:12:32,540
Would you tell Rachel?
但请你告诉瑞秋好吗？

219
00:12:33,210 --> 00:12:35,940
All right. At least I'm prepared.
好啦，至少我现在有准备 好

220
00:12:37,650 --> 00:12:39,050
Oh,yes.
漂亮

221
00:12:41,060 --> 00:12:43,790
-They're not for you. Are you upset? -I am now.
不是给你的，你有不开心吗？ 现在有了

222
00:12:46,690 --> 00:12:48,130
Hey,roomie.
室友 

223
00:12:48,530 --> 00:12:50,190
Okay,bye.
好，再见

224
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:58,830
There's something important I have to tell you.
瑞秋，我有重要的事要告诉你

225
00:12:59,040 --> 00:13:00,340
Are you pregnant?
你怀孕了？

226
00:13:01,580 --> 00:13:03,480
No, but I'm throwing this shirt away.
没有，但我要扔掉这件衣服

227
00:13:05,250 --> 00:13:08,480
I think there was a little misunderstanding before.
刚才有一些误会

228
00:13:09,050 --> 00:13:14,080
When I said that Chandler and I wanted to live together...
我说钱德和我想住在一起

229
00:13:14,560 --> 00:13:17,520
we meant alone together.
意思是只有我们两个人

231
00:13:21,560 --> 00:13:24,730
Oh,my God. That's funny. I can't believe I did that.
天哪，真好笑，我居然会误会

232
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:27,700
No, sweetie. You know what? This is my fault.
不，是我不好 

233
00:13:27,900 --> 00:13:29,530
I wasn't clear.
我没说清楚

234
00:13:29,740 --> 00:13:31,760
I'm really sorry.
真的很抱歉

235
00:13:32,510 --> 00:13:35,940
Listen,you take as much time as you need to move out, okay?
你可以慢慢找房子 

236
00:13:36,180 --> 00:13:37,910
There's absolutely no rush.
一点也不用急

237
00:13:39,110 --> 00:13:40,380
Okay.
好

238
00:13:43,856 --> 00:13:45,380
好

239
00:13:47,390 --> 00:13:48,910
Don't you want a cookie?
你不吃饼干吗？

240
00:13:49,860 --> 00:13:51,020
Sure.
好啊

241
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:54,620
Thanks.
谢谢 

242
00:13:54,860 --> 00:13:56,230
Do you need a tissue?
需要面纸吗？

243
00:14:00,270 --> 00:14:02,790
-Where did you get these? -I made them.
这是哪里的饼干？ 我做的

244
00:14:03,040 --> 00:14:05,730
Oh, God, they're so yummy!
天哪，真好吃

245
00:14:08,680 --> 00:14:11,270
-Okay, whose is this? -That's mine.
这是谁的？ 我的

246
00:14:11,450 --> 00:14:13,780
-And what about this? Whose is this? -That's mine.
那这个呢？ 也是我的

247
00:14:13,950 --> 00:14:17,210
Okay, whose dishwashing soap is this?
那这罐洗碗精呢？

248
00:14:17,380 --> 00:14:20,720
That was here when we moved in.
我们搬进来时就有了

249
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:25,290
Oh,I guess it really is concentrated.
难怪浓成这样

250
00:14:28,030 --> 00:14:31,490
It's gonna be weird when I come home and you're not here.
以后我回家你就不在了

251
00:14:31,800 --> 00:14:33,530
No more Joey and Chan's.
没有乔伊和钱德家了 

252
00:14:33,800 --> 00:14:35,960
No more J and C's.
没有乔和钱家了

253
00:14:36,370 --> 00:14:39,640
Want to go to Joey and Chandler's? Can't. It's not there.
“要不要去乔伊和钱德家？” “不行，已经不在了”

254
00:14:40,570 --> 00:14:43,980
I'll be across the hall. We can still do all the same stuff.
我只是搬到对面 我们还是可以跟以前一样

255
00:14:44,210 --> 00:14:47,040
We won't be able to have those long talks at night...
但以后就不能半夜起来 

256
00:14:47,250 --> 00:14:49,220
about our feelings and the future.
促膝长谈感觉和未来了

257
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:51,840
Not once did we do that.
我们一次也没做过

258
00:14:52,990 --> 00:14:56,720
Don't you remember that night, it was late and I was feeling sick...
不是有一次很晚了，我不舒服

259
00:14:56,890 --> 00:15:01,890
and you said I would feel better tomorrow?
你说我“明天”就会好一点？

260
00:15:02,060 --> 00:15:03,760
Oh, yeah. I remember that.
对，我记得

261
00:15:04,300 --> 00:15:08,030
I don't know. I'm just gonna miss living with you.
我会想念那些事 

262
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:10,230
Yeah,me too,man.
我也是

263
00:15:10,840 --> 00:15:13,900
-What the hell is that? -That's disgusting.
那是什么？ 好恶心

264
00:15:17,510 --> 00:15:20,610
I told Rachel that it's just gonna be the two of us.
我告诉瑞秋我们要自己住了 

265
00:15:20,880 --> 00:15:23,180
Oh,yeah? Well,how'd she take it?
是吗？她还好吗？

266
00:15:23,750 --> 00:15:24,950
Really well.
非常好

267
00:15:25,750 --> 00:15:27,280
Surprisingly well.
令人意外的好

268
00:15:27,550 --> 00:15:30,790
She didn't cry. She wasn't angry or sad.
没有哭，也没有生气或难过

269
00:15:33,690 --> 00:15:37,130
And you're upset because you didn't make your best friend cry?
你很不爽没把手帕交弄哭？

270
00:15:37,930 --> 00:15:40,260
All I'm asking for is a little emotion.
我只求一点真情流露 

271
00:15:40,470 --> 00:15:42,590
Is that too much to ask after six years?
我们6年室友耶

272
00:15:42,870 --> 00:15:45,600
What,are Rachel and l not as close as you guys?
我们没你们要好吗？ 

273
00:15:45,810 --> 00:15:49,940
I mean,did we not have as much fun? Don't I deserve a few tears?
没你们开心吗？ 我不值得她掉几滴泪吗？

275
00:15:51,380 --> 00:15:53,370
When we told Joey, he cried his eyes out.
乔伊一听到就哭得死去活来

276
00:15:54,780 --> 00:15:57,380
I did not cry my eyes out!
我才没有哭得死去活来

277
00:15:57,950 --> 00:16:00,080
Come on, it's like the end of an era.
这就像一个时代的结束 

278
00:16:00,290 --> 00:16:02,220
No more J-Man and Channy's!
再也没有乔兄和钱哥了

279
00:16:04,220 --> 00:16:06,450
Okay,I gotta ask,who calls us that?
我一定要问 有谁那样叫我们？

280
00:16:13,100 --> 00:16:15,300
You got married again?
你又结婚了

281
00:16:16,400 --> 00:16:17,430
Yes.
对

282
00:16:18,340 --> 00:16:21,830
So that's your second marriage in two years?
这是你2年内第二次结婚

283
00:16:22,110 --> 00:16:24,410
Yes. Second in two years.
对，2年两次

284
00:16:24,650 --> 00:16:26,980
Third,overall.
总共三次

285
00:16:27,750 --> 00:16:30,480
I have been a divorce attorney for 23 years...
罗斯，我当了23年离婚律师 

286
00:16:30,750 --> 00:16:33,810
and never have I had so much business from one client.
没有一个客户比你捧场

287
00:16:35,760 --> 00:16:38,590
Why don't you tell me what happened?
告诉我怎么回事

288
00:16:39,490 --> 00:16:43,290
Basically,Rachel and I were in Vegas,a nd we got drunk.
基本上，瑞秋和我在赌城 我们喝醉了…

289
00:16:43,500 --> 00:16:46,860
I'm sorry, is this the same Rachel whose name you said...
抱歉，她就是你上次结婚 

290
00:16:47,130 --> 00:16:48,970
at the altar in the second marriage?
叫错的那个瑞秋？

291
00:16:49,170 --> 00:16:50,860
Yes,yes,yes.
对

292
00:16:51,270 --> 00:16:53,170
But I do not love her.
但是我并不爱她

293
00:16:54,680 --> 00:16:56,300
That's better then.
这就好多了

294
00:16:57,780 --> 00:17:01,210
This was just a drunken mistake, and I need to get it annulled.
这只是酒醉犯错，我要办注销 

295
00:17:01,480 --> 00:17:02,540
I see.
我懂了

296
00:17:03,050 --> 00:17:05,640
Have you considered therapy?
你考虑过接受治疗吗？

297
00:17:07,550 --> 00:17:11,350
I think just the annulment for today.
我想今天办注销就好了

298
00:17:11,660 --> 00:17:13,960
-There are some forms to fill out. -Easy.
要填几份表格 简单

299
00:17:14,230 --> 00:17:18,630
We'll need witnesses who can testify that you were not of sound mind.
必须有证人证明 你们当时神智不清

300
00:17:18,830 --> 00:17:20,700
No problem.
没问题

301
00:17:20,970 --> 00:17:24,130
We'll need you and Rachel to testify before a judge.
你和瑞秋得向法官说明

302
00:17:27,810 --> 00:17:30,070
There's no way to do this without her?
不能不找她吗？ 

303
00:17:30,340 --> 00:17:34,210
Because I kind of already told her it was taken care of.
我已经告诉她事情都办妥了

304
00:17:34,420 --> 00:17:36,410
Of course you did.
你当然这么说

305
00:17:38,320 --> 00:17:42,690
Look, you can't get an annulment unless you and Rachel are both there.
罗斯，你和瑞秋都在场 才能办理注销

306
00:17:44,530 --> 00:17:47,650
What about someone who looks like Rachel?
那找一个长得像瑞秋的人呢？

307
00:17:49,230 --> 00:17:51,200
I will think about the therapy.
我会考虑接受治疗

308
00:17:58,910 --> 00:18:03,240
So I was thinking that maybe we should start dividing up our stuff.
我想我们应该开始分东西了

309
00:18:03,940 --> 00:18:05,340
Okay.
好

310
00:18:05,910 --> 00:18:07,780
No point in dragging it out.
没必要拖拖拉拉的

311
00:18:08,380 --> 00:18:11,510
Dragging out the long process of you moving out...
我是说你搬走

312
00:18:11,720 --> 00:18:13,850
and us not living together anymore.
我们分开的事

313
00:18:14,326 --> 00:18:15,623
好

315
00:18:20,930 --> 00:18:23,450
What about this? Who gets this?
瑞秋，这个要归谁？

316
00:18:23,700 --> 00:18:27,430
I don't know if I want it because it might be too many memories.
我不知道我想不想要 它有太多回忆

317
00:18:29,100 --> 00:18:30,630
-What is that? -I don't know.
那是什么？ 我不知道

318
00:18:34,210 --> 00:18:37,040
How about this? I want you to have the big plate.
瑞秋，大盘子呢？ 我要你留着大盘子

319
00:18:38,080 --> 00:18:41,310
Wow, Monica, thanks. I love this plate.
谢谢，我很喜欢这个盘子

320
00:18:41,720 --> 00:18:44,450
Something to remember me by.
这样你就会记得我

321
00:18:45,750 --> 00:18:48,380
Mon, you're not dying. I'm just moving out.
你又不是快死了 我只是要搬出去

322
00:18:49,320 --> 00:18:51,810
We're gonna see each other all the time.
我们还是会天天见面

323
00:18:52,160 --> 00:18:54,990
But still,it's a big change.
但这是个大转变 

324
00:18:55,260 --> 00:18:58,430
The end of an era, you might say.
甚至是一个时代的结束

325
00:19:01,300 --> 00:19:03,170
Are you okay? You're not blinking.
你还好吗？眼睛都没眨

326
00:19:04,400 --> 00:19:08,570
I'm fine. I was thinking about how it's an end of an era.
我很好 我只是在想一个时代要结束了

327
00:19:09,010 --> 00:19:10,600
Oh,all right.
好吧

328
00:19:12,480 --> 00:19:16,640
But I gotta say, I don't think six years counts as an era.
但老实说 6年应该称不上一个时代

329
00:19:16,950 --> 00:19:19,780
An era is defined as a significant period of time.
一个时代就是一段重要的日子

330
00:19:20,020 --> 00:19:23,420
It was significant for me. Maybe it wasn't significant to you!
我觉得重要 或许你不觉得重要

331
00:19:23,620 --> 00:19:27,030
-What is the matter with you? -What is the matter with you?!
你是怎么了？ 你才怎么了？

332
00:19:28,460 --> 00:19:30,020
Why aren't you more upset?
你为什么没有更不开心？ 

333
00:19:30,300 --> 00:19:33,320
Aren't you gonna be sad that we're not living together?
我们要分开了你不难过吗？

334
00:19:33,630 --> 00:19:35,530
Aren't you gonna miss me at all?
你都不会想我吗？

335
00:19:35,870 --> 00:19:38,700
Monica, all right. But don't get mad at me.
好吧，说出来你别生气

336
00:19:40,440 --> 00:19:43,030
It's just a little hard to believe.
我只是有点难以相信 

337
00:19:43,810 --> 00:19:45,210
What's hard to believe?
难以相信什么？

338
00:19:45,450 --> 00:19:49,640
I mean,it's you guys. You do this kind of stuff,you know?
你们啊，你们就是这样

339
00:19:49,850 --> 00:19:53,950
You were gonna get married in Vegas, and then you backed out.
你们在赌城说要结婚又不结了

340
00:19:54,190 --> 00:19:58,630
I'm not upset because I don't see you going through with it. I'm sorry.
我并不认为你们会真的同居 对不起

342
00:20:04,730 --> 00:20:06,700
It's going to happen.
瑞秋，事情已经确定了

343
00:20:07,170 --> 00:20:08,530
Chandler will move in here.
钱德会搬进来

344
00:20:08,740 --> 00:20:11,640
-But I.. -I know,just let me finish, okay?
但是… 你先听我说完

345
00:20:12,570 --> 00:20:16,340
This isn't something that we just impulsively decided to do in Vegas.
这不是在赌城的一时冲动 

346
00:20:16,580 --> 00:20:19,070
This is something that we both really want.
我们真的想要住在一起

347
00:20:20,880 --> 00:20:23,250
And it is going to happen.
我们会住在一起 

348
00:20:24,080 --> 00:20:25,480
It is?
是吗？

349
00:20:27,650 --> 00:20:28,990
Really?
真的？ 

350
00:20:29,390 --> 00:20:31,080
Yeah,sweetie.
没错

351
00:20:32,860 --> 00:20:36,760
You mean,we're not gonna live together anymore?
我们不能再住在一起了？

352
00:20:38,237 --> 00:20:39,795
不行了

353
00:20:42,440 --> 00:20:45,200
Oh,my God. I'm gonna miss you so much.
天哪，我会好想你 

354
00:20:45,410 --> 00:20:47,200
I'm gonna miss you.
我也是

355
00:20:48,440 --> 00:20:50,100
I mean, it's the end of an era!
这是一个时代的结束 

356
00:20:50,380 --> 00:20:51,870
I know!
我知道

357
00:20:55,350 --> 00:20:57,750
-Okay, bye. -Oh,no.
再见 又来了

358
00:20:58,450 --> 00:21:00,750
So did you get the annulment?
你去办注销了吗？ 

359
00:21:00,950 --> 00:21:04,080
-I couldn't. -I knew it. Because you love Rachel.
我办不了 我就知道，因为你爱瑞秋

360
00:21:04,890 --> 00:21:07,860
It's not that. Annulments are more complicated..
不是那样的 事情比想像中复杂…

361
00:21:08,060 --> 00:21:10,290
Complicated because of the love.
爱让它变得复杂

362
00:21:10,760 --> 00:21:13,360
I do not love Rachel.
我不爱瑞秋

363
00:21:13,630 --> 00:21:15,530
I'm telling her about the whole thing...
我现在就去告诉她 

364
00:21:15,770 --> 00:21:19,030
so we can get this marriage annulled as fast as possible.
好尽快把手续办好

365
00:21:19,270 --> 00:21:21,210
Would I do that if I loved her?
我如果爱她会这么做吗？

366
00:21:21,410 --> 00:21:24,400
I've never been more convinced of your love for her.
我现在更确信你爱她

367
00:21:24,780 --> 00:21:28,870
I do not have feelings for Rachel, okay?
我对瑞秋没有感觉，好吗？

368
00:21:32,050 --> 00:21:34,420
Oh,what's wrong?
怎么了？

369
